Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
timing_extract..._scalar_tables(25.10)  timing_extract..._scalar_tables(25.10)

Name
       timing_extract_model_write_clock_checks_as_scalar_tables

Syntax
       timing_extract_model_write_clock_checks_as_scalar_tables

       {true | false}

       Default: false

       Allows  the  extracted timing model to write the minimum pulse width or
       minimum period checks as scalar arcs.

       To set this global variable, use the set command.

